-- Aaron acquires Progressive Finance Holdings for $700 mln
-- By Shailaja Sharma in Bangalore
-- Tue Apr 15, 2014 07:17AM EDT
-- None



April 15 (Reuters) - Aaron's Inc <AAN.N>, a rent-to-own furniture and electronics retailer, said it will buy Progressive Finance Holdings Llc from private equity firm Summit Partners for about $700 million in cash.

Aaron's said it expects the deal to add to its cash earnings per share from 2014. [ID:nPn7Mky2Z]